g title=&quot;比亚迪G6改版谍照&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px none;&quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/19/1392799222785.jpg&quot; /></a></p><p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;&quot;>【<a class=&quot;notfirstlink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/model_2490/&quot;>比亚迪</a>改版<a class=&quot;notfirstlink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/model_2490/&quot;>G6</a>普通版前脸谍照 格栅细节升级,采用了飞翼式的立体造型】</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;&quot;>  当然在整车结构方面我们不要奢望有任何改变,这不属于<a class=&quot;notfirstlink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/model_2490/&quot;>比亚迪</a>的强项,一般情况下,一个平台一旦成型,<a class=&quot;notfirstlink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/model_2490/&quot;>比亚迪</a>会持续改进并借助平台共享的原则推出多个全新版本,而此次出现的改版<a class=&quot;notfirstlink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/model_2490/&quot;>G6</a>其实另有目的&mdash;&mdash;为2.0TiD做相应的准备;这是基于254期<a class=&quot;firstLink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: rgb(59, 89, 152);&quot; href=&quot;http://goche.auto.sohu.com/newcar/&quot;>新车</a>准入目录中<a class=&quot;notfirstlink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/model_2490/&quot;>G6</a>一个格栅小改版本做出的推断,格栅粗看之下与现销版<a class=&quot;notfirstlink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/model_2490/&quot;>G6</a>相同,但是格栅细节明显做了较大的改动,采用了飞翼式的立体造型。&nbsp;</p><p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;&quot;><a target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/model_2490/pic_t2372545.shtml&quot;><img title=&quot;比亚迪 G6 实拍 外观 图片&quot; alt=&quot;比亚迪 G6 实拍 外观 图片&quot; width=&quot;292&quot; height=&quot;196&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px none;&quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/19/1392799222932.jpg&quot; /></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/model_2490/pic_t2372544.shtml&quot;><img title=&quot;比亚迪 G6 实拍 外观 图片&quot; alt=&quot;比亚迪 G6 实拍 外观 图片&quot; width=&quot;292&quot; height=&quot;196&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px none;&quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/19/1392799222977.jpg&quot; /></a></p><p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;&quot;>【2013款<a class=&quot;notfirstlink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/model_2490/&quot;>比亚迪G6</a>】</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;&quot;>  外观方面的改动其实就是前保险杠的修改,由于进气格栅与前保险杠采用的是一体式设计方案,因此改动起来相对便利,这也是为何前大灯不做修改的主要原因,进气格栅的改动相对耀眼,巨大的镀铬边框,内嵌蜂窝式格栅,并且还做了镀化处理,思路上来说,类似<a class=&quot;firstLink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: rgb(59, 89, 152);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/model_1015/&quot;>锐志</a>普通与运动版的区别,因此<a class=&quot;notfirstlink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/model_2490/&quot;>G6</a>改为这样的进气格栅明显也是吸取了相同的想法,运动版就要体现的更为霸气。</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;&quot;>  其它的改动如<a class=&quot;firstLink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: rgb(59, 89, 152);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/baike/37.shtml&quot;>雾灯</a>框尺寸加大,并且特意将边框外凸,以便显示强劲的肌肉感觉,而裙边则借助黑色导流边条加以承托,运动范十足。轮毂也特意更改为风火轮式的造型,类似<a class=&quot;firstLink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: rgb(59, 89, 152);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/model_3894/&quot;>G5</a>那样的轮毂风格,明显偏向运动化,这与车头造型的修改意图相契合。</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; text-align: center;&quot;><a target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/photo_1020/pic2822312.shtml&quot;><img title=&quot;比亚迪G6改版谍照&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px none;&quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/19/1392799223261.jpg&quot; /></a></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; text-align: center;&quot;>【轮毂更改为风火轮式的造型,明显偏向运动化,这与车头造型的修改意图相契合】</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;&quot;>  尾部造型没有出现明显的变化,不过尾部<a class=&quot;firstLink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: rgb(59, 89, 152);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/baike/142.shtml&quot;>排量</a>标识则出现了2.0TID的字样,说明整车采用的是最新开发的2.0Ti直喷增压<a class=&quot;firstLink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: rgb(59, 89, 152);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/baike/250.shtml&quot;>发动机</a>,搭配的自然是<a class=&quot;firstLink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: rgb(59, 89, 152);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/baike/104.shtml&quot;>双离合变速器</a>。</p><p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;&quot;><a target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/photo_1020/pic2786418.shtml&quot;><img title=&quot;新款比亚迪G6谍照&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px none;&quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/19/1392799223319.jpg&quot; /></a></p><p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;&quot;>【<a class=&quot;notfirstlink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/model_2490/&quot;>比亚迪</a>改版<a class=&quot;notfirstlink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/model_2490/&quot;>G6</a><a class=&quot;notfirstlink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/baike/250.shtml&quot;>发动机</a>舱布局】</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;&quot;>  不过这个2.0Ti<a class=&quot;notfirstlink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/baike/250.shtml&quot;>发动机</a>目前还没有现身目录,说明此款<a class=&quot;notfirstlink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/baike/250.shtml&quot;>发动机</a>还处于路试阶段,当然2.0Ti的标识算是首次现身实车。同样出现的还有<a class=&quot;notfirstlink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/baike/250.shtml&quot;>发动机</a>舱布局,虽然凌乱,但是加上<a class=&quot;notfirstlink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/baike/250.shtml&quot;>发动机</a>罩之后就会规整很多,根据官方公布的数据,2.0Ti的参数为<a class=&quot;firstLink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: rgb(59, 89, 152);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/baike/144.shtml&quot;>最大功率</a>155Kw/6000rpm,峰值扭矩为<a class=&quot;firstLink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: rgb(59, 89, 152);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/model_2571/&quot;>350</a>Nm/1<a class=&quot;firstLink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: rgb(59, 89, 152);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/model_3516/&quot;>500</a>~4200rpm,不过功率参数是报出的<a class=&quot;notfirstlink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/baike/144.shtml&quot;>最大功率</a>,实际功率需要下调,当然要申报数据为准,例如1.5Ti的功率为113Kw,实际功率则是105Kw。</p><p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;&quot;><a target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/photo_1020/pic2786419.shtml&quot;><img title=&quot;新款比亚迪G6谍照&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px none;&quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/19/1392799223898.jpg&quot; /></a></p><p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;&quot;>【尾部后保险杠上的双排气管轮廓,由圆形改为刀锋式样,<a class=&quot;notfirstlink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/baike/142.shtml&quot;>排量</a>标识为2.0TID字样】</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;&quot;>  尾部唯一的修改就是后保险杠上的双排气管轮廓,由圆形更改为刀锋式样,其实还是圆形,只不过排气口加装了装饰件;通过中控下端透露的造型细节来看,改动的可能性很小,可能会针对操作面板做适当的色调处理,整体框架不做变动。</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;&quot;>  由于未在<a class=&quot;notfirstlink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://goche.auto.sohu.com/newcar/&quot;>新车</a>目录中现身,因此其最终的上市时间还难以判断,此外这也不排除是<a class=&quot;firstLink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: rgb(59, 89, 152);&quot; href=&quot;http://auto.sohu.com/beijingchezhan/&quot;>北京车展</a>先期展示车的可能,预计正式量产还需时日,同样是申报很久的1.2Ti至今都未上市销售,更别说是从未在目录现身的2.0Ti,正式上市时间只能留待<a class=&quot;notfirstlink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: initial; outline: none medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot; href=&quot;http://db.auto.sohu.com/model_2490/&quot;>比亚迪</a>官方给予准确的答案。</p>
